title: D3 Adc sucht nach einem team
body:
I am a D3 Adc looking for a team.
24 years old and from austria.

I am looking for a serious team with scrims, analysis, a coach if possible and preferably in a league.

I am/have:
-Fluent english and german
-Reliable and hardworking
-Available every day 
-Very vocal 
-Tilt proof/strong mental
-Decent team experience 
-Highly motivated 
-Good champion pool 
-Easy to work with
-Thriving to improve

Feel free to DM me with offers or questions cheers.
